hexstaff.basic.crude.name=Crude Hex Staff
hexstaff.basic.crude.description=A knotted branch still weeping sap, bound with rawhide. Barely more than a dowsing rod -- but it hums.
hexstaff.basic.bronze.name=Bronze Hex Staff
hexstaff.basic.bronze.description=Cast in the first forges, its warmth smells of smoke and ambition.
hexstaff.basic.copper.name=Copper Hex Staff
hexstaff.basic.copper.description=Veined with patina. Lightning-hungry, conducts thought as readily as current.
hexstaff.basic.iron.name=Iron Hex Staff
hexstaff.basic.iron.description=Plain, honest, unremarkable. The apprentice's staff -- until it isn't.
hexstaff.basic.thorium.name=Thorium Hex Staff
hexstaff.basic.thorium.description=Green-cored and restless. Old apothecaries carved these from storm-fallen yew.
hexstaff.basic.cobalt.name=Cobalt Hex Staff
hexstaff.basic.cobalt.description=Cold to the touch even at noon. Deepwater stone drinks the sun.
hexstaff.basic.adamantite.name=Adamantite Hex Staff
hexstaff.basic.adamantite.description=Forged where the mountain bleeds. The haft remembers every oath sworn over it.
hexstaff.basic.mithril.name=Mithril Hex Staff
hexstaff.basic.mithril.description=Weighs less than thought. Elder-crafters tuned each rod to a single chord.
hexstaff.basic.onyxium.name=Onyxium Hex Staff
hexstaff.basic.onyxium.description=Carved from the hollow between stars. Whoever carries it is already partway gone.
